MrTarget v3.0.1
=====================================================================
Copyright (C) 2014 Lock of War, Developmental (Pty) Ltd

RAID STYLE ENEMY UNIT FRAMES in BATTLEGROUNDS
POKEMON NAME for RUSSIAN TARGET CALLING

Supports Warlords of Draenor v6.2.0

CHECK OUT THE ADDON IN ACTION ON OUR YOUTUBE CHANNEL
http://youtube.com/c/lockofwar 

SEND BUGS or FEATURE REQUESTS TO
http://twitter.com/renevatium OR mrtarget@lockofwar.com

WANT to BETA TEST NEW VERSIONS? We always need testers: mrtarget@lockofwar.com 

Display all enemy unit frames up to a maximum of 15
Right-click drag to MOVE (only while options panel is open)
Units are sorted ALPHABETICALLY, then by CLASS, then by ROLE
Objectives frame will be collapsed during battle
To avoid taint, options that alter the UI are disabled during battle

MORE FEEDBACK PLEASE!
We want to hear you ideas/issues

SLASH COMMANDS
---------------------------------------------------------------------
/mrtarget, /mrt hide|show - Quick hide/show for during battle
/mrtarget, /mrt - Open interface options panel

